com.alexkasko.unsafe.offheap
Interface OffHeapDisposable

All Known Implementing Classes:
OffHeapLongArray, OffHeapLongArrayList, OffHeapPayloadArray, OffHeapPayloadArrayList, OffHeapPayloadIntArray, OffHeapPayloadIntArrayList, OffHeapPayloadLongArray, OffHeapPayloadLongArrayList, OffHeapStructArray, OffHeapStructArrayList
public interface OffHeapDisposable

Basic interface for off-heap classes that support manual memory freeing. Not freed memory will be released on OffHeapMemory (impl) instances garbage collection.

alexkasko Date: 3/5/13
